### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Verify email (copy token from email)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verify?token={{verificationToken}}

### Login as a verified user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Use the returned JWT for authenticated requests
### Replace {{token}} with the `token` from the login response
### Example: list locations for current user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Who am I? (useful for debugging auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add a location (requires Bearer token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/locations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Home",
  "city": "Colombo",
  "latitude": 6.9271,
  "longitude": 79.8612,
  "default": true
}
